txt.en: 'Pretty soon we'll have enough force to take over this whole region.'
'Yeah, we'll get rid of the Rangers, then all the loot of the old ruins will be ours!'
'Ost Forod will be ours too, soon enough.'
'Don't worry about the Rangers. There aren't enough of them to fight us anymore.'
'Let the Gauradan stay in their hills. They're no concern of mine.'
